    "Try fewer words or choose another index or category." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the empty state when the user has a search query but no results.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Tshunhue" : {
      "comment" : "A dialog box that appears when an error occurs.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Tshunhue has no accounts, analytics, advertising, or telemetry. Catalogs and images are requested directly from the HTTPS hosts you configure, so those hosts receive ordinary network information such as your IP address. Search history and recent transfers remain on this device. Tshunhue does not inspect or transmit text typed with its keyboard extension." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tshunhue 沒有帳號、分析、廣告或遙測功能。目錄與圖片會直接向您設定的 HTTPS 主機要求，因此這些主機會收到您的 IP 位址等一般網路資訊。搜尋紀錄與最近傳送項目只會留在這台裝置上。Tshunhue 不會檢查或傳送您使用鍵盤延伸功能輸入的文字。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tshunhue has no accounts, analytics, or telemetry. Source and image hosts receive ordinary network requests when content is synchronized or displayed." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tshunhue 沒有帳號、分析或遙測功能。同步或顯示內容時，資料來源與圖片主機會收到一般網路要求。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "URL" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "網址"
          }
        }
